nodes.text: Jeffrey Arnold "Jeff" Moss was an American composer, lyricist, playwright and television writer, best known for his work on the children's television series Sesame Street. In 1985, Moss composed the song "My Star" for Ewoks: The Battle for Endor, a made-for-TV film set in the Star Wars universe. Moss died of colon cancer at age 56 in 1998.
